item.title: How do i make a ladder that teleports you somewhere?
item.dc:creator: @John459 John459
item.description:
@John459 wrote:

Yes they do. Here is how to choose the ladder’s location.
Open client.java and search for

public void NewObjects() {

Scroll down until you see something like this:

makeGlobalObject(2444, 3085, 2213, 0, 10); // bank

Add this code under one of them:

makeGlobalObject(####, ####, ####, 0, 10); // ladder

Change the first set of #s to the x coord of where you want the ladder to be.
Change the second set of #s to the y coord you want the ladder to be.
Change the third set of #s to the object id of the ladder.

Read full topic

item.title: How do i make a ladder that teleports you somewhere?
item.dc:creator: @John459 John459
item.description:
@John459 wrote:

Type control+f and search for

OBJECT CLICK ONE

Copy and paste this code below it.

case ###: // your ladder sendMessage("You climb the ladder."); teleportToX = ####; teleportToY = ####; break;

Change the first set of #s to the object id of the ladder.
Change the second set of #s to the x coord of where you want the ladder to take you.
Change the third set of #s to the y coord of where you want the ladder to take you.
